column1: # The physical locations of oNCOs found in the probands of this study are supplied in
# this file along with information about the number of MPPs within the oNCO, family
# size and whether oNCO is unambiguously assigned to owner. Ambiguously assigned
# oNCOs are not used for analysis of allele selection bias and DNMs colocation.
# The data columns are as follows:
# Begin (GRCh38 position of earliest converted variant in oNCO),
# End (GRCh38 position of last converted variant in oNCO),
# ptype (transmitting parent, P: paternal, M: maternal),
# gcMPPs (number of gene-converted MPPs within oNCO),
# sibs (number of siblings with same parents),
# AO (ambiguous owner of oNCO - only in 2-children families),
